00:27:23.000 --> 00:27:28.000
You can see that when you read the mantras, you know, and the goddess always has to wear a sari.

137
00:27:28.000 --> 00:27:32.000
That's, you know, that's something it has to be like that.

138
00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:41.000
And in India, all the ladies learn from their mothers that they have to also wear a lot of jewelry with the sari because the goddess also did.

139
00:27:41.000 --> 00:27:46.000
