140
00:27:46.000 --> 00:28:05.000
So mother had a tremendous respect for the sari really and for these traditions, so much so that on one occasion we all came to a puja.

141
00:28:05.000 --> 00:28:08.000
I think it was Birmingham was it?

142
00:28:08.000 --> 00:28:09.000
Birmingham, yes.

143
00:28:10.000 --> 00:28:13.000
And suddenly the puja was about to start.

144
00:28:13.000 --> 00:28:15.000
We were all dressed in our pajama quarters.

145
00:28:15.000 --> 00:28:19.000
The ladies were dressed in their saris.

