00:28:19.000 --> 00:28:26.000
Everything was ready. Mother was sitting on the stage and then mother asks, you know, do you have a sari for the puja?

147
00:28:26.000 --> 00:28:33.000
And the leader said, well, as a matter of fact, the person bringing the sari got detained is a problem.

148
00:28:33.000 --> 00:28:35.000
And mother said, okay, that's no problem.

