00:28:35.000 --> 00:28:39.000
But if there's no puja, if there's no sari, no puja.

150
00:28:39.000 --> 00:28:40.000
It's as simple as that.

151
00:28:40.000 --> 00:28:43.000
So why don't we do the puja the next day?

