00:28:44.000 --> 00:28:50.000
This was a big shock because we were all dressed and ready and some people don't like a change of plan.

153
00:28:50.000 --> 00:28:56.000
But mother said, look, you know, don't be upset for the change of plan because this is a lot of fun.

154
00:28:56.000 --> 00:28:58.000
It's nice to have a change of plan.

155
00:28:58.000 --> 00:29:01.000
And now I'm going to enjoy myself, mother said.

156
00:29:01.000 --> 00:29:05.000
And she went to her handbag, got her glasses.

157
00:29:05.000 --> 00:29:10.000
And now I'm going to see how the ladies look so beautiful in their saris, you know,

158
00:29:10.000 --> 00:29:16.000
and how the gentlemen also are looking so nice in their silks and pijama quarters and all that, you know.

159
00:29:16.000 --> 00:29:24.000
And so they changed the lighting, you know, instead of the light being towards Shri Mataji on the stage to the yogi.

160
00:29:24.000 --> 00:29:26.000
So mother could see the sari yogis now.

161
00:29:26.000 --> 00:29:32.000
And she said she was really enjoying seeing all the ladies in their saris, how beautiful they look, you know.

162
00:29:32.000 --> 00:29:39.000
So mother is always giving compliments to the Indian ladies or the size of the Guinness for wearing the saris.

163
00:29:39.000 --> 00:29:41.000
She's very pleased when they do.

164
00:29:41.000 --> 00:29:48.000
But as she said, you see, no sari, you know, if there's no sari, you cannot have a puja.

165
00:29:48.000 --> 00:29:50.000
These are very important traditions.

166
00:29:50.000 --> 00:29:52.000
There was another puja this time.

167
00:29:52.000 --> 00:29:55.000
It was in, where?

168
00:29:55.000 --> 00:29:57.000
Chelsea, I don't know.

169
00:29:57.000 --> 00:29:59.000
I think it was in Hampstead.

