00:46:58.000 --> 00:46:59.000
No.

306
00:46:59.000 --> 00:47:02.000
I said, well, I can teach you how to cook.

307
00:47:02.000 --> 00:47:11.000
And mother taught him how to cook professionally, you know, in two weeks, you know, and mother used to be very proud of that, that he learned to cook everything perfectly in two weeks.

